<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CafeButter Pastry Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f1e5;
            color: #5c3d2e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #5c3d2e;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #8b5e3b;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #5c3d2e;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #8b5e3b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        CafeButter Pastry Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">

        <h2>Pastries</h2>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Croissant <span class="price">₹120</span></h3>
            <p>A classic French pastry, buttery, flaky, and golden brown.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Pain au Chocolat <span class="price">₹140</span></h3>
            <p>Similar to a croissant but filled with rich, dark chocolate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Danish Pastry <span class="price">₹130</span></h3>
            <p>A buttery, flaky pastry often filled with fruit or cream cheese.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Eclair <span class="price">₹150</span></h3>
            <p>A choux pastry filled with custard and topped with chocolate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Madeleine <span class="price">₹110</span></h3>
            <p>Small, shell-shaped sponge cakes with a hint of lemon.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Tart <span class="price">₹160</span></h3>
            <p>Open-faced pastry with sweet or savory fillings.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Cinnamon Roll <span class="price">₹130</span></h3>
            <p>Soft dough rolled with cinnamon, sugar, and topped with icing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Brioche <span class="price">₹120</span></h3>
            <p>A rich, buttery, slightly sweet bread-like pastry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Scone <span class="price">₹100</span></h3>
            <p>Dense, crumbly British pastry, often served with jam.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Baklava <span class="price">₹180</span></h3>
            <p>A Middle Eastern delight with layers of filo, nuts, and honey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Churros <span class="price">₹140</span></h3>
            <p>Crispy, deep-fried dough pastries rolled in sugar and cinnamon.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Financier <span class="price">₹130</span></h3>
            <p>A small almond-flavored cake with a crisp exterior and soft center.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
